Weeks 11‚Äì14: Evaluate performance and prepare for scale.



---

Why It Matters

This targeted approach unlocks additional risk coverage without expanding operational volume drastically. By turning known SARs into beacons, the organisation can uncover hidden suspicious activity, sharpen typology coverage, and strengthen financial crime defence.

